entries.journal_entry_description: Full-scale war demands armaments, and Lieutenant Pofko has ordered you to create 5 E-11 carbines for the Imperial Army.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You have been tasked with creating 5 E-11 carbines for the Imperial Army.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have completed the carbines for the troops in Restuss and should return to Lieutenant Pofko with them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Give the 5 carbines to the load lifter droid.
